<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Katie Price treated her daughter Princess to a pamper session on Friday. </p>

<p>The former glamour model, 42, is recovering from the surgery she underwent earlier this month after breaking her ankle and feet in a horror accident during a holiday.</p>

<p>As she remains wheelchair bound, her daughter, 13, who she shares with ex Peter Andre, was pushing her into the salon, where they got matching hairdos.</p>

<p>Out and about: Katie Price treated her daughter Princess to a pamper session on Friday</p>

<p>Katie looked in high spirits as she appeared with her daughter, who proved the apple doesn't fall from the tree as she was snapping selfies just like her mum. </p>

<p>The glamour model was wearing a blue tracksuit, while Princess wore a bright yellow jumper with a contrasting crimson scrunchie ahead of her makeover. </p>

<p>Earlier in the week, Katie received a hot pink scooter to travel around in as she continues to recover from an operation on her broken feet. </p>

<p>The star will now be able to travel around near her home on the scooter. She is currently in the middle of a two year driving ban.</p>

<p>Ouch: The former glamour model, 42, is recovering from the surgery she underwent earlier this month after breaking her ankle and feet in a horror accident during a holiday</p>

<p>Sleek: As she remains wheelchair bound, her daughter, 13, who she shares with ex Peter Andre, was pushing her into the salon, where they got matching hairdos</p>

<p>Bonding session: Katie looked in high spirits as she appeared with her daughter, who proved the apple doesn't fall from the tree as she was snapping selfies just like her mum</p>

<p>A source told MailOnline: 'Katie will be able to claim back a bit of independence. The scooter has been given a total make over by Robbie at Valetmagic... </p>

<p>'He reached out to Katie offering his team to work their magic, putting a smile back on her face will certainly be speeding up her recovery.'</p>

<p>The star added to The Sun: 'I won't be breaking any speed limits on this - that's for sure.' The scooter has been customised to Katie's standards and features a 'Pricey' registration plate. </p>

<p>Lady in blue: The glamour model was wearing a blue tracksuit, while Princess wore a bright yellow jumper with a contrasting crimson scrunchie ahead of her makeover</p>

<p>Glammed up: Princess looked overjoyed with her hairdo</p>

<p>Sleek: Princess was having a full blowdry like her mum</p>

<p>Long hair don't care: Katie appeared to be having extensions put in</p>

<p>Katie recently revealed she was stepping out of the spotlight on Thursday on medical advice as she has been told to 'rest in order to heal'.</p>

<p>Amid the social media hiatus, Katie appeared in a promotional fake tan video shared on her Instagram on Sunday evening - with her representatives confirming this was a pre-scheduled post. </p>

<p>They said: 'I can confirm that Katie has not returned to social media.  Katie's team posted the Instagram and this was not posted by Katie herself.</p>

<p>'It was filmed prior to her hiatus.'  </p>

<p>Heading out: Katie recently revealed she was stepping out of the spotlight on Thursday on medical advice as she has been told to 'rest in order to heal'</p>

<p>A helping hand: Their friend helped push her pink wheelchair </p>

<p>Sleek: They both looked glam as they emerged </p>
